{"tid":2288991,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓 BTS 屌打哂日本奶共組合！","createTime":"2020-11-17T02:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T02:37:33.000Z","uid":118346,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16161e9fa2f958919b503cb8e5d543f8e0c3c579","tid":2288991,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T02:37:33.000Z","msg":"<em>韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）上月因提及韓戰而被內地小粉紅轟辱華，之後其所屬事務所又推出印有反送中時常用口號「be water」的樽裝水，舉動引發小粉紅在網上狂攻擊，不過已打開歐美市場的BTS冇有怕，近日事務所推出的新宣傳片中，除出現穿上黃色連帽外套的公仔被一群藍衣人包圍外，成員柾國又在另一宣傳片中穿黑衣兼拿着黃色雨傘現身，之後片中更出現黃色雨傘陣，網民認為連串舉動加起來，不是巧合那麼簡單！</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201117/QA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ/?fbclid=IwAR3V8Og-GQ9XW9yFr7zK30T2XXzX1kGj82i94Qdnrn9w_ZWuh-VYEA5eZcc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201117%2FQA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3V8Og-GQ9XW9yFr7zK30T2XXzX1kGj82i94Qdnrn9w_ZWuh-VYEA5eZcc&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=a408e378\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201117%2FQA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3V8Og-GQ9XW9yFr7zK30T2XXzX1kGj82i94Qdnrn9w_ZWuh-VYEA5eZcc&h=1c4474d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201117/QA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ/?fbclid=IwAR3V8Og-GQ9XW9yFr7zK30T2XXzX1kGj82i94Qdnrn9w_ZWuh-VYEA5eZcc</a>"}]}